#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:4
msgid "Features"
msgstr "功能"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:6
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of the commonly used features of both C# and "
"Godot and how they are used together."
msgstr "本页概述了C#和Godot的常用功能以及它们如何一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:12
msgid "Type conversion and casting"
msgstr "类型转换和强制转换"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:14
msgid ""
"C# is a statically typed language. Therefore, you can't do the following:"
msgstr "C#是一种静态类型语言。因此，您无法执行以下操作："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:21
msgid ""
"The method ``GetNode()`` returns a ``Node`` instance. You must explicitly "
"convert it to the desired derived type, ``Sprite`` in this case."
msgstr ""
"方法 ``GetNode()`` 返回一个 ``Node`` 实例。在这种情况下，您必须将其显式转换为"
"所需的派生类型， ``Sprite``。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:24
msgid "For this, you have various options in C#."
msgstr "为此，在C#中有多种选择。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:26
msgid "**Casting and Type Checking**"
msgstr "**强制转换和类型检查**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:28
msgid ""
"Throws ``InvalidCastException`` if the returned node cannot be cast to "
"Sprite. You would use it instead of the ``as`` operator if you are pretty "
"sure it won't fail."
msgstr ""
"如果返回的节点无法转换为Sprite，则抛出 ``InvalidCastException`` 。如果您非常"
"确定它不会失败，您可以使用它而不是 ``as`` 运算符。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:36
msgid "**Using the AS operator**"
msgstr "**使用AS运算符**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:38
msgid ""
"The ``as`` operator returns ``null`` if the node cannot be cast to Sprite, "
"and for that reason, it cannot be used with value types."
msgstr ""
"如果节点无法转换为 ``Sprite``，则 ``as`` 运算符返回 ``null``，因此，它不能与"
"值类型一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:47
msgid "**Using the generic methods**"
msgstr "**使用泛型方法**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:49
msgid ""
"Generic methods are also provided to make this type conversion transparent."
msgstr "还提供了泛型方法以使该类型转换透明。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:51
msgid ""
"``GetNode<T>()`` casts the node before returning it. It will throw an "
"``InvalidCastException`` if the node cannot be cast to the desired type."
msgstr ""
"``GetNode <T>()`` 在返回之前强制转换节点。如果节点无法强制转换为所需类型，它"
"将抛出一个 ``InvalidCastException``。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:58
msgid ""
"``GetNodeOrNull<T>()`` uses the ``as`` operator and will return ``null`` if "
"the node cannot be cast to the desired type."
msgstr ""
"``GetNodeOrNull <T>()`` 使用 ``as`` 运算符，如果节点无法强制转换为所需类型，"
"则返回 ``null``。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:66
msgid "**Type checking using the IS operator**"
msgstr "**使用IS运算符进行类型检查**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:68
msgid ""
"To check if the node can be cast to Sprite, you can use the ``is`` operator. "
"The ``is`` operator returns false if the node cannot be cast to Sprite, "
"otherwise it returns true."
msgstr ""
"要检查节点是否可以强制转换为 ``Sprite``，可以使用 ``is`` 运算符。如果节点无法"
"转换为 ``Sprite``，则 ``is`` 运算符返回 ``false``，否则返回 ``true``。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:79
msgid ""
"For more advanced type checking, you can look into `Pattern Matching "
"<https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/csharp/pattern-matching>`_."
msgstr ""
"对于更高级的类型检查，您可以查看 `模式匹配 <https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/"
"dotnet/csharp/pattern-matching>`_。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:84
msgid "C# signals"
msgstr "C# 信号"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:86
msgid ""
"For a complete C# example, see the **Handling a signal** section in the step "
"by step :ref:`doc_scripting` tutorial."
msgstr ""
"有关完整的C#示例，请参阅逐步 :ref:`doc_scripting` 教程中的 **处理信号** 部"
"分。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:88
msgid ""
"Declaring a signal in C# is done with the ``[Signal]`` attribute on a "
"delegate."
msgstr ""
"在C#中声明一个信号是通过一个 ``delegate`` 上的 ``[Signal]`` 属性完成的。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:98
msgid ""
"These signals can then be connected either in the editor or from code with "
"``Connect``. If you want to connect a signal in the editor, you need to "
"(re)build the project assemblies to see the new signal. This build can be "
"manually triggered by clicking the “Build” button at the top right corner of "
"the editor window."
msgstr ""
"这些信号然后可以在编辑器中或通过带有 ``Connect`` 的代码连接。如果要在编辑器中"
"连接信号，则需要（重新）构建项目程序集以查看新信号。单击编辑器窗口右上角的“构"
"建”按钮可以手动触发此构建。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:119
msgid "Emitting signals is done with the ``EmitSignal`` method."
msgstr "发射信号是通过 ``EmitSignal`` 方法完成的。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:129
msgid ""
"Notice that you can always reference a signal name with the ``nameof`` "
"keyword (applied on the delegate itself)."
msgstr ""
"请注意，您始终可以使用 ``nameof`` 关键字引用信号名称（应用于 ``委托"
"（delegate）`` 本身）。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:131
msgid ""
"It is possible to bind values when establishing a connection by passing an "
"object array."
msgstr "建立连接时可以通过传递对象数组来绑定值。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:151
msgid ""
"Signals support parameters and bound values of all the `built-in types "
"<https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/csharp/language-reference/keywords/"
"built-in-types-table>`_ and Classes derived from :ref:`Godot.Object "
"<class_Object>`. Consequently, any ``Node`` or ``Reference`` will be "
"compatible automatically, but custom data objects will need to extend from "
"`Godot.Object` or one of its subclasses."
msgstr ""
"信号支持所有 `内置类型 <https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/csharp/"
"language-reference/keywords/built-in-types-table>`_ 的参数和绑定值，以及从 :"
"ref:`Godot.Object <class_Object>` 派生的类。因此，任何 ``Node`` 或 "
"``Reference`` 将自动兼容，但是自定义数据对象将需要从 ``Godot.Object`` 或其子"
"类之中扩展。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:163
msgid ""
"Finally, signals can be created by calling ``AddUserSignal``, but be aware "
"that it should be executed before any use of said signals (with ``Connect`` "
"or ``EmitSignal``)."
msgstr ""
"最后，可以通过调用 ``AddUserSignal`` 来创建信号，但要注意它应该在使用所述信号"
"之前执行（使用 ``Connect`` 或 ``EmitSignal``）。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:174
msgid "Preprocessor defines"
msgstr "预处理器定义"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:176
msgid ""
"Godot has a set of defines that allow you to change your C# code depending "
"on the environment you are compiling to."
msgstr "Godot有一组定义，可让您根据要编译的环境来更改C#代码。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:179
msgid ""
"If you created your project before Godot 3.2, you have to modify or "
"regenerate your `csproj` file to use this feature (compare "
"``<DefineConstants>`` with a new 3.2+ project)."
msgstr ""
"如果您在Godot 3.2之前创建了项目，则必须修改或重新生成 ``csproj`` 文件才能使用"
"此功能（将 ``<DefineConstants>`` 与一个新的3.2+项目进行比较）。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:184
msgid "Examples"
msgstr "示例"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:186
msgid "For example, you can change code based on the platform:"
msgstr "例如，您可以根据平台更改代码："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:203
msgid ""
"Or you can detect which engine your code is in, useful for making cross-"
"engine libraries:"
msgstr "或者，您可以检测代码所在的引擎，这对于创建跨引擎库很有用："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:219
msgid "Full list of defines"
msgstr "定义的完整列表"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:221
msgid "``GODOT`` is always defined for Godot projects."
msgstr "总是为Godot项目定义 ``GODOT``。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:223
msgid ""
"One of ``GODOT_64`` or ``GODOT_32`` is defined depending on if the "
"architecture is 64-bit or 32-bit."
msgstr "根据体系结构是64位还是32位，定义了 ``GODOT_64`` 或 ``GODOT_32`` 之一。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:225
msgid ""
"One of ``GODOT_X11``, ``GODOT_WINDOWS``, ``GODOT_OSX``, ``GODOT_ANDROID``, "
"``GODOT_HTML5``, or ``GODOT_SERVER`` depending on the OS. These names may "
"change in the future. These are created from the ``get_name()`` method of "
"the :ref:``OS <class_OS>`` singleton, but not every possible OS the method "
"returns is an OS that Godot with Mono runs on."
msgstr ""
"取决于操作系统，``GODOT_X11``、``GODOT_WINDOWS``、``GODOT_OSX``、"
"``GODOT_ANDROID``、``GODOT_HTML5``、或 ``GODOT_SERVER`` 之一。这些名称将来可"
"能会更改。这些是从 :ref:`OS <class_OS>` 单例的 ``get_name()`` 方法创建的，但"
"并非该方法返回的每个可能的操作系统都是运行Godot和Mono的操作系统。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:230
msgid ""
"When **exporting**, the following may also be defined depending on the "
"export features:"
msgstr "**导出** 时，还可以根据导出功能定义以下内容："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:232
msgid ""
"One of ``GODOT_PC``, ``GODOT_MOBILE``, or ``GODOT_WEB`` depending on the "
"platform type."
msgstr ""
"取决于平台类型，``GODOT_PC``、``GODOT_MOBILE``、或 ``GODOT_WEB`` 之一。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:234
msgid ""
"One of ``GODOT_ARM64_V8A`` or ``GODOT_ARMEABI_V7A`` on Android only "
"depending on the architecture."
msgstr ""
"Android上的 ``GODOT_ARM64_V8A`` 或 ``GODOT_ARMEABI_V7A`` 之一，仅取决于架构。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:236
msgid ""
"One of ``GODOT_S3TC``, ``GODOT_ETC``, or ``GODOT_ETC2`` depending on the "
"texture compression type."
msgstr ""
"``GODOT_S3TC``、``GODOT_ETC``、或 ``GODOT_ETC2`` 中的一种，取决于纹理压缩类"
"型。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/getting_started/scripting/c_sharp/c_sharp_features.rst:238
msgid ""
"Any custom features added in the export menu will be capitalized and "
"prefixed: ``foo`` -> ``GODOT_FOO``."
msgstr ""
"在导出菜单中添加的所有自定义功能都将大写并加前缀：``foo`` -> ``GODOT_FOO``。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "These signals can then be connected either in the editor or from code "
#~ "with ``Connect``."
#~ msgstr "然后可以在编辑器中或通过 ``Connect`` 连接代码连接这些信号。"
